702
01:27:52,704 --> 01:27:54,789
That motorboat -

703
01:27:54,956 --> 01:27:56,791
has it come to help us?

704
01:27:56,958 --> 01:27:59,294
No. It is from Ginostra.

705
01:27:59,419 --> 01:28:02,422
- What is Ginostra?
- Ginostra is a village...

706
01:28:02,547 --> 01:28:04,674
the other side of the island.

707
01:28:04,799 --> 01:28:06,801
<i>II</i> [Continues]

708
01:28:58,186 --> 01:29:00,230
<i>II</i> [Continues]

709
01:29:26,172 --> 01:29:27,966
[Sicilian ]

710
01:29:39,811 --> 01:29:41,688
See?
Our home is safe.

711
01:29:41,813 --> 01:29:43,439
Yes.

712
01:29:55,743 --> 01:29:58,329
Listen, I want to talk to you.

713
01:29:58,454 --> 01:30:00,582
I don't want
to stay here any longer.

714
01:30:00,707 --> 01:30:02,417
So?

715
01:30:02,542 --> 01:30:04,586
So I want to go away.

716
01:30:07,422 --> 01:30:10,592
- I don't want to have a child here.
- Eal/ora?

717
01:30:12,093 --> 01:30:14,053
And?

718
01:30:14,179 --> 01:30:16,181
And I'm leaving.
I'm going crazy here.

719
01:30:18,933 --> 01:30:21,102
Rather than have
a child on this island, I'd -

720
01:30:21,227 --> 01:30:24,439
- During the eruption of '30 <i>-
- </i> I saw enough yesterday.

721
01:30:24,606 --> 01:30:26,524
I'm not interested in 1930.

722
01:30:29,235 --> 01:30:31,779
I'm going.
Nothing can keep me here.

723
01:30:31,946 --> 01:30:33,281
But, Karin, listen -

724
01:30:33,448 --> 01:30:35,074
Give me what money you have.

725
01:30:35,200 --> 01:30:37,577
I hope you won't refuse me.
It's so little anyway.

726
01:30:37,702 --> 01:30:41,247
- Yes, too little.
- I know, but I'm not afraid to face life, as long as I'm free...

727
01:30:41,372 --> 01:30:44,459
as long as I can fight
and defend myself.

728
01:30:44,584 --> 01:30:46,377
I know it.

729
01:30:46,502 --> 01:30:49,589
You're not going
to keep me here, are you?

730
01:30:49,714 --> 01:30:52,133
It's no use looking
at me that way!

731
01:30:52,300 --> 01:30:55,136
It won't do you any good!

732
01:30:55,261 --> 01:30:57,472
Nothing can keep me here!

733
01:31:58,074 --> 01:31:59,909
Antonio!

734
01:32:00,034 --> 01:32:03,579
Go down to the well and get me
some water. I want to wash.

735
01:32:10,920 --> 01:32:13,172
Did you hear me?

736
01:32:13,298 --> 01:32:15,216
<i>[ Hammering ]</i>

737
01:32:26,102 --> 01:32:27,729
Antonio!

738
01:32:27,895 --> 01:32:30,064
<i>Antonio!</i>

739
01:32:30,231 --> 01:32:33,026
Antonio! Antonio!

740
01:32:34,652 --> 01:32:38,114
What are you doing?
Open up!

741
01:32:38,239 --> 01:32:40,533
Antonio!
What's the matter with you?

742
01:32:40,658 --> 01:32:42,493
Open up the door!

743
01:32:44,454 --> 01:32:46,205
Antonio!

744
01:33:25,203 --> 01:33:27,830
<i>[ Karin ]
Hello! Hello!</i>

745
01:33:27,955 --> 01:33:30,958
You! You!

746
01:33:40,635 --> 01:33:42,303
Come. Come closer.

747
01:33:44,514 --> 01:33:46,307
Can you hear me?

748
01:33:46,474 --> 01:33:48,184
I need help.
I can't get out.

749
01:33:48,309 --> 01:33:51,479
My husband nailed the door
from the outside. I need help.

750
01:33:51,646 --> 01:33:54,607
- Why he do that?
- Get me out. <i>I'll</i> tell you later.

751
01:33:54,732 --> 01:33:56,984
Come around.
The stairway's on the other side.

752
01:34:05,159 --> 01:34:07,245
- Oh, thank you.
- What happened?

753
01:34:07,370 --> 01:34:09,831
Let's not talk here.
It's dangerous. Come.

754
01:34:31,811 --> 01:34:33,521
Nice, isn't it?

755
01:34:35,273 --> 01:34:37,233
It's peaceful here.

756
01:34:38,526 --> 01:34:39,861
Let's sit down.

757
01:34:42,780 --> 01:34:44,782
